OL,4,CUK tourism spending 'worth just half of
OL,5,Cpre-pandemic level'
OL,6, UK tourism is set for a slow recovery
OL,7, from the pandemic, with spending by
OL,8, holidaymakers this year expected to be
OL,9, just half the level of 2019.
OL,11,FForecasts by the VisitBritain agency
OL,12,Findicate that domestic tourism will be
OL,13,Fworth #51.4bn in 2021, down from
OL,14,F#91.6bn two years ago.
OL,16,FIts forecast for spending by foreign
OL,17,Ftourists in the UK is #6.2bn, less than
OL,18,Fa quarter of the #28.4bn in 2019.
OL,20,FThe predictions come as UK tourism
OL,21,Fchiefs prepare for a summit on Tuesday.
